\c 34 Zedhckia ano udzwa zvichaitirwa Jerusaremu 3 A Shoko, rakasvika kuna Jere" miya, richibva kuna Jehovha, pa nguva iyo Nebhukadhinezari mambo weBhabhironi, nehondo yake yose, noushe hwose hwenyika hwakanga hwakabatwa naye, namarudzi ose, vachirwa neJerusaremu namaguta ose aro, richiti, 2 "Zvanzi naJehovha, Mwari waIsiraeri, `Enda, undotaura naZedhekia mambo waJudha; uti kwaari, `Zvanzi naJehovha, tarira, ndichaisa guta rino muruoko rwamambo weBhabhironi, iye ucharipisa nomoto; 3 newe haungapukunyuki paruoko rwake, asi zvirokwazvo uchabatwa, nokuiswa muruoko rwake; meso ako achaona meso amambo weBhabhironi, muchataurirana nemiromo yenyu, iwe uchaenda Bhabhironi.' 4 Asi chinzwa shoko raJehovha, iwe Zedhekia mambo waJudha, zvanzi naJehovha pamusoro p√•lco, iwe haungaurawi nomunondo; 5 iwe uchafa norugare; sezvavakapisira madzimababa ako, iwo madzimambo akare akakutangira, saizvozvo vachakupisirawo; vachakuchema vachiti, `Haiwa ishe!' Nokuti ndini ndakataura shoko iro, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha." 6 Ipapo muporofita Jeremiya akataura mashoko aya ose kuna Zedhekia mambo waJudha paJerusaremu, 7 nenguva yakarwa honao yamambo weBhabhironi neJerusaremu uye namaguta ose aJudha akanga asara, neRakishi neAzeka, nokuti ndiyo yakanga yasara pamaguta aJudha, ari maguta akakombwa norusvingo.
